{"word":"G3887 - παραμένω - paraménō - par-am-en'-o - Abide","slug":"G3887","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραμένω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>paraménō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>par-am-en'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abide"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - parameno&#x0304;</b> - <i>par-am-en'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G3306\">G3306</a>; to <i>stay near</i>, that is, <i>remain</i> (literally <i>tarry</i>; or figuratively <i>be permanent</i>, <i>persevere</i>): - abide, continue."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1696\">G1696</a>, <a href=\"#/G3306\">G3306</a>, <a href=\"#/G3438\">G3438</a>, <a href=\"#/G4037\">G4037</a>, <a href=\"#/G5278\">G5278</a>, <a href=\"#/G5281\">G5281</a>"}]}